<b>TK Soccer — Version 0.7.0 (Pre-Alpha)</b>

This update focuses on <b>progression, rewards, shop systems, 
premium content, UI polish, and significantly improved ball physics.</b>

<b>🎁 NEW: Player Progression & Reward System</b>

<b>🆙 Level-Up Rewards</b>
• Players now earn <b>rewards when leveling up</b>
• Milestone levels can grant <b>random cosmetic rewards</b>
• Rewards are clearly displayed on a redesigned end screen

<b>🎉 New Reward Reveal Screen</b>
• Brand-new <b>reward reveal animations</b> at the end of matches
Items now display:
• Rarity color backgrounds
• Rarity badges
• Improved title rendering
• Cleaner animations and transitions

<b>🎲 Random Item Drops</b>
• Random rewards now use a <b>weighted rarity system</b>
• Certain items are excluded from random drops to preserve rarity

<b>💰 Starting Economy Update</b>
• New players now start with <b>500 Cash</b>
• Economy and item ownership logic improved for reliability

<b>🛒 Shop & Premium Store Overhaul</b>

<b>🏪 Daily Rotating Shop</b>
• Shop rotates items daily using improved calculation logic
• Weighted rarity system for fair rotation
• Ownership validation improved to prevent duplicate purchases

<b>💎 Premium Store Added</b>
• New <b>Premium Store</b> for game passes and developer products
• Improved item previews with character model display
• Better hover effects and ownership indicators
• Cleaner confirmation dialogs with preview support

<b>🪙 Developer Product Support</b>
Developer product purchases now:
• Process correctly
• Grant coins instantly
• Validate securely server-side

<b>👕 Customisation & Character Improvements</b>

<b>🔢 Kit Number System</b>
• Players can now set their <b>Kit Number</b>
• Includes increment/decrement UI and confirmation system
• Fully customizable

<b>🎭 Celebration Previews</b>
• Celebrations can now be previewed in menu
• Improved visibility handling during cinematics
• Character properly restores after preview

<b>🧢 Accessory Cleanup</b>
• Non-essential accessories removed on spawn for 
cleaner visuals and performance

<b>🎮 Controller & Input Improvements</b>
• Improved <b>gamepad support</b>
• D-Pad tool switching
• Proper PlayStation & Xbox input prompts
• Cleaner tool activation handling
• Refined set piece action bindings
• Free kick and penalty prompts now display correctly

<b>⚽ Major Ball Physics Upgrade</b>

<b>🔧 Shot Tuning</b>
• Increased maximum shot power
• Adjusted gravity scaling for low-angle shots
• Reduced excessive spin for better balance
• Improved ball rotation syncing

<b>🧠 Smarter Foul Logic</b>
• Advantage and foul awarding now better account for ball ownership

<b>🎥 Match & End Screen Improvements</b>
• Match timer consistency fixed
• Scoreboard stability improved
• Reward pages integrated into match completion flow
• Debug trajectory disabled for live builds

<b>🖥️ UI & Menu Polish</b>
• Cleaner menu transitions and camera positioning
• Backpack handling unified across systems
• Improved panel color distinction (Premium clearly highlighted)
• Lighting and post-processing tuned for clarity

<b>📢 Pitchside Advertisements</b>
• New dynamic pitchside ads
• Smooth animated transitions
• Expanded variety of advertisement boards

<b>🛠️ Performance & Stability</b>
• Improved memory cleanup across UI systems
• Fixed tooltip connection leaks
• Removed obsolete assets and debug warnings
• Improved profile loading reliability
• Balanced skill move force calculations

<b>Summary</b>
This update introduces:
• Real progression with meaningful rewards
• A fully upgraded shop and premium system
• Significantly improved and more realistic ball physics

More updates coming soon ⚽
